OL,3,CThree drug arrests after man dies near
OL,4,Cthe Royal Welsh Show
OL,6,FA 25 year old man has died at a farm
OL,7,Fnear the Royal Welsh Show.
OL,9,FDyfed-Powys Police said they were
OL,10,Fcalled to Penmaenau Farm, Llanelwedd
OL,11,Fat around 10.30pm on Saturday 18 July
OL,12,Fto reports of a medical emergency.
OL,14,FA 25 year old man was pronounced dead
OL,15,Fat the site, near the Royal Welsh
OL,16,Fshowground.
OL,18,FThe force said three people have been
OL,19,Farrested on suspicion of drug-related
OL,20,Foffences and remain in custody.
