OL,3,CThree drug arrests after man dies near
OL,4,Cthe Royal Welsh Show
OL,6,FIn a statement the Royal Welsh Show
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are deeply saddened by this
OL,8,Ftragic news, and our thoughts are with
OL,9,Fthe young man's family and friends,
OL,10,Fand with everyone affected by this
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,F"We will continue to support Dyfed-
OL,14,FPowys Police as their enquiries
OL,15,Fcontinue."
